<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4814] Starting an online alter when regions are splitting can leave their daughters unaltered</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4814</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve seen a situation where regions were splitting almost exactly at the same time as an alter command was issued and those regions&apos; daughters were left unaltered. It would even seem that the daughters&apos; daughters also share this situation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reopening all the regions fixes the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
